WEBVTT


00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:00.940
I, I don't.

00:00:00.941 --> 00:00:03.600
I don't care that we're different.

00:00:03.860 --> 00:00:06.640
You know, I. What I care about

00:00:07.940 --> 00:00:10.280
is you. I care about you,

00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:12.900
okay?

00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:16.320
And I didn't say it.

00:00:16.940 --> 00:00:21.440
I should have said it, but I didn't because,

00:00:23.140 --> 00:00:24.260
uh. Well,

00:00:24.261 --> 00:00:30.160
ha ha. Cause I am an emotionally insecure source of your discomfort.

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:33.040
He's not good at expressing his feelings.

00:00:34.780 --> 00:00:36.860
Probably because I've been on my own my whole life.

00:00:36.861 --> 00:00:38.380
It's not an excuse. It's just.

00:00:38.381 --> 00:00:39.360
It's why,

00:00:39.820 --> 00:00:44.940
instead of telling you that you're the best thing that ever happened to me, I.

00:00:44.941 --> 00:00:47.300
I make jokes about your ears and.

00:00:47.301 --> 00:00:49.140
And I tell you that you try too hard

00:00:49.141 --> 00:00:50.820
when you know the truth is.

00:00:50.821 --> 00:00:54.840
I just don't want you to get hurt because.

00:00:56.260 --> 00:01:02.040
Because no one else in the world matters more to me than you do.
